data.description: Welcome to this charming townhome that epitomizes modern living! Step inside and be greeted by the captivating beauty of this updated home. The first floor boasts high ceilings and gorgeous ceramic tile plank "wood" flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere that is cozy with a contemporary flair. The living room is a haven of comfort, featuring built-in shelves and seamlessly flowing into the dining area, perfect for entertaining. Prepare to be impressed by the U-shaped kitchen. It comes equipped with a built-in microwave, a smooth top range, and a convenient pantry for your storage needs. This townhome offers a unique dual primary suite layout, with one primary suite located on each floor. Whether you prefer the convenience of a ground-floor suite or the elevated privacy of the second level, you'll find comfort and style in both. The loft, serving as a second living area, provides flexibility for your lifestyle, whether you envision it as a game room, home gym, or a tranquil retreat.  In addition to updated flooring, the Seller has revitalized the downstairs bathroom, replaced the AC and water heater, as well as completing the look with fresh paint!
